                          zinc-maven-plugin

  This Maven¹ plugin compiles Java² and Scala³ sources.  It’s very simple to
  use, providing almost no configuration options, relying on the user to instead
  specify the command-line options to use for each compiler as they see fit.

¹ Read more about Maven on its homepage at http://maven.apache.org
² The Java language: https://java.com/en/
³ The Scala language: https://www.scala-lang.org
